3.6        Bushiroad International may also disclose your Personal Information to third parties if Bushiroad International believes that doing so is appropriate to comply with the law, to enforce or exercise Bushiroad International’s rights, or to protect Bushiroad International’s, Bushiroad International’s users’ or third parties’ property, rights or safety.

